title: The Gronk-less Super Bowl Media Night, Brady's Beef, and the Left-Handed Eagles | GM Street (Ep. 230)
description:
The Ringer's Michael Lombardi and Tate Frazier discuss a happy, stylish Bill Belichick (07:30), Tom Brady's issue with radio station WEEI (10:00), the surprisingly calm Eagles (14:15), the Minnesota fans in attendance (27:30), and wrist surgery for Blake Bortles (30:15).
